Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:12.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,turned to rubber after \Nhe ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwith Trafalgar Law and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They freed the toys who had been forced to\Nlabor as slaves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Doflamingo trapped everybody in the country in the Birdcage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's bring an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's started...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll pay 100 million berries for each star rating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And put prices on the heads of Luffy and 11 others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hajrudin! If you kill Straw Hat,\Nyou'll get a lot of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a pittance!\NI almost had my pride stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but was saved by God Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can truly win my pride back,\Nonly by repaying my debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I will take down Doflamingo!\N--No, {\i1}I{\i0} will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, it's me!\N--No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Go away"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} will kick Mingo's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's massive! We're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Grizzly Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's the stone man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time we've seen him\Nin a human-like figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, leave it up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain has no business with\Na worthless rock like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all you've got. Live with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You soprano-voiced dumb-ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Shocking Confession!\NLaw's Soulful Vow!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0} stopped moving\Nafter his head fell off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The monster stopped moving! Is he dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, whatever happened to him,\Nif he's not gonna throw those annoying punches,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now is the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring down Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's me!\N--No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those jerks are coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop them!\NDon't let them get to the Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring out more worthwhile guys to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can't stop the group of fighters from the Colosseum.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! How vigorous they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they still wanna mess with the Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So reckless-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Groups of Navy soldiers led by
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujitora are coming together in front of the Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"G"roups of Navy soldiers! There's the "G"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastille's unit will join us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half of all Navy soldiers are already\Nin front of the Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was Straw Hat and the others\Nthat stopped Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are four different groups or individuals\Napproaching the Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, the group of tough men from around the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who fought in the Colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second, the former commander of the King Riku Army and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the strongest man in the history of the Colosseum - Kyros.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give yourself up, Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before we're all dead\Nif we don't catch you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:08:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need you 12 criminals to\Nsacrifice yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, third, No.2 of the Straw Hats - Pirate Hunter Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fourth, Straw Hat Luffy and the traitor - Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Keep going, Moocy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah! Go, bull!\N--Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, how much longer are you gonna stay on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NJust get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're kidding, Straw Hat-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see Señor anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was with us just a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI think he went to look for that pervert-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Per...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...vert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SMILE factory! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, break open, door to the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Radical Bea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that crappy attack won't even harm the factory but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I just came to finish up my business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have to fight an enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what men do, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Señor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Kyros!\NCome on out and surrender yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna come get you if you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not doing this for money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done, we all have to kill each other until no one's left!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just wanna bring an end to this nightmare\Nas soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to bring an end to this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame you for your decision but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that means I need to get going even faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shoot!\N--Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that I need to do, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing great, Moocy! You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get to Mingo before anyone else like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:11:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Mingo!\NI'm not gonna let them do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat the hell out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-{\i1}san{\i0}, your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stayed all by himself to\Nfight such a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be alright! He's not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill you, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, your voice is so squeaky and annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIt makes my ears tickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, soprano-voiced old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made a vow! He'll never be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the only way for us to survive now is to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan that I suggested to you guys was
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto take down Doflamingo indirectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, to be honest, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...want to hurt him directly, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was beaten earlier but I won't be this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13 years ago, there was a person I adored
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Doflamingo killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Corazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The former top executive of\Nthe Doflamingo Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Was he a member of his clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he was.\NHe also saved my life and was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Doflamingo's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...biological young brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}'s not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "Of course"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy wouldn't stay in the same place\Neven for five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Freedom! Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the King of the Pirates should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that stone monster?!\NKing Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Royal Palace up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Viola-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it, Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key to Trafalgar Law's handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found it with my Clairvoyance!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to deliver it to them somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Viola!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they so important to you?!\NThey're pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're unlawful men - who will break\Nthis country's deceptive peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}, I decided to trust them,\Nthe Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government gave him the title of the Warlord
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that pirate Doflamingo reigned this country with terror,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,causing us so much pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want the help of the Navy, that was supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,supporting justice, or the Government after all these years!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't hear them!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The voices of the people who fell victim because of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The angry voices of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People in authority often only hear\Nwhat they want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, the words of Straw Hat and the others are humane
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they take actions\Nout of the goodness of their hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll kick Doflamingo's ass for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stay with my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIf I stop now, what's gonna happen to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}! King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Five-star man, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Usoland aka God Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man risked his life
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and broke the spell of toys\Nthat had been
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,overshadowing this country for a decade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland! Usoland! Usoland! Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland! Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His bravery moved us to tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, really, really,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we were so touched by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a superhero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:20:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland! Usoland! Usoland! Usoland! Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Luffyland is the superhero's captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats aka Usolanders are Dressrosa's hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're pirates,\Nwe're gonna trust them to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Straw Hats' unforgettable moving scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky I am to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland! Usoland! Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland! Usoland! Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Viola-{\i1}san{\i0},\Ncan I go deliver the key to Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stay here and wait!\NLet me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's do it!\NLet's go see Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you, of course! Count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca! You're a criminal in Doflamingo's game!\NIf you go down to the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--they won't leave you alone!\N--I'm gonna be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Cub-{\i1}san{\i0}!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are planning on going,\Nlet's use the rooftops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cub-{\i1}san{\i0} and I will go along with you!\NSo don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rooftops?!\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inhel, can I leave the factory in your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the scouting unit,\NFraland is fighting Señor Pink now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Fraland, we Tontattas will all work together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take back Princess Mancherie and our people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you guys later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody! We don't have that much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you all again here on the King's Plateau!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Straw Hat Luffy... What a strange man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even in this desperate situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone finds hope in the Straw Hats without them realizing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pirates, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Straw Hat-{\i1}san{\i0}, we're almost at the first level!\N--There are so many enemies there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's…\N--Something's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're the first to arrive!\NNo one's here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:22:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Moocy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:23:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's Straw Hat Luffy!\N--Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.18,0:23:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fire Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Keep up the pace, Moocy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others keep making smooth progress!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the Navy led by Fujitora starts chasing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.02,0:23:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when they close in on Luffy and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\None man stands in the Navy's way on his own!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.94,0:23:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The strongest forces of the Revolutionary Army\Nand the Navy finally face off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Big Collision! Chief of Staff - Sabo vs. Admiral Fujitora!”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.17,0:23:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.59,0:23:49.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
